Text: Re NPC Interconnection Agmt and MOU Cc a couple items to change on the MOU and then it is ready to go We should be able to get it to NPC today Jim Gilbert AM To Don CT cc Mary CT Ed Clark Dale CT Jody CT Subject NPC Interconnection Agmt and MOU Don Where are you with providing comments back to NPC on the Interconnection agreement did this get issued Also where do we stand on the MOU with NPC Its important relative to our schedule that these items keep moving Please advise Jim
